\begin_layout Standard
To implement the BFGS algorithm, it suffices to compute 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(J^{(k)}\right)^{-1}\nabla f(x^{(k)})$
\end_inset

.
 Therefore, we can directly use the recursive formula (
